1
00:00:01,587 --> 00:00:02,985
How's Jimmy today?
Jimmy今天怎么样了?

2
00:00:03,799 --> 00:00:05,787
Better. Thank you, Doctor.
他好些了. 谢谢您, 医生.

3
00:00:07,525 --> 00:00:10,760
Can I see him please, Mrs. Williams?
我可以看看他吗, Williams夫人?

4
00:00:12,111 --> 00:00:13,690
Certainly, doctor.
当然可以, 医生.

5
00:00:14,050 --> 00:00:14,688
Come upstairs.
上楼吧.

6
00:00:16,235 --> 00:00:18,152
You look very well, Jimmy.
你看上去很好, Jimmy.

7
00:00:19,704 --> 00:00:20,704
You are better now,
你现在好些了,

8
00:00:21,326 --> 00:00:23,480
but you mustn't get up yet.
但你还不应该起床.

9
00:00:25,362 --> 00:00:29,495
The boy mustn't go to school yet, Mrs. Williams.
这孩子还不能去上学, Williams夫人，

10
00:00:30,299 --> 00:00:33,034
And he mustn't eat rich food.
而且不能吃油腻的食物.

11
00:00:33,889 --> 00:00:37,077
Does he have a temperature, doctor?
他还发烧吗, 医生?

12
00:00:37,594 --> 00:00:38,819
No, he doesn't.
不, 他不发烧了.

13
00:00:39,955 --> 00:00:42,240
Must he stay in bed?
他还必须卧床吗?

14
00:00:43,285 --> 00:00:48,017
Yes. He must remain in bed for another two days.
是的. 他还必须卧床两天.

15
00:00:49,525 --> 00:00:53,767
He can get up for about two hours each day,
他每天可以起来两个小时,

16
00:00:54,572 --> 00:00:57,697
but you must keep the room warm.
但您必须保持房间温暖.

17
00:00:58,544 --> 00:01:01,497
Where's Mr. Williams this evening?
Williams先生今晚去哪儿了?

18
00:01:02,188 --> 00:01:04,460
He's in bed, doctor.
他在床上呢, 医生.

19
00:01:05,600 --> 00:01:07,693
Can you see him please?
您能看看他吗?

20
00:01:08,911 --> 00:01:11,843
He has a bad cold, too!
他也得了重感冒!

